Class ModifiedConditionDecisionCoverageParser

All Implemented Interfaces:
ICodeCoverageParser
public class ModifiedConditionDecisionCoverageParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICodeCoverageParser

Instances of this interface are used in order to parse a tree consisting of IExecutionNode instances, and return a subset of those nodes based on some criteria.

The common use of such parsers in KeYTestGen is to guarantee a certain degree of code coverage for the code being tested. The returned set of nodes will in this case form a basis for a test suite which will satisfy the targeted code coverage criteria.
